{"id":6328,"type":2,"name":"The Fan and the Flower","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/b2/94/6328_Qlf8S.jpg","rating":{"total":44,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":1,"6":6,"7":19,"8":9,"9":5,"10":3},"score":7.4},"summary":"　　从前有个配有电灯的老式吊扇，和他的主人（一个老妇人）住在老旧的公寓里。公寓的生活宁静、枯燥，吊扇孤零零地呆在屋顶，倍感无聊。\r\n　　某天老妇人带来一盆花，花儿的到来让吊扇倍感兴奋，他用尽各种办法展示自己，以期引起花儿的注意。花儿从最初的矜持，慢慢为吊扇的热情所触动，爱情之花盛情绽放。他们从未接触彼此，就在这咫尺之间遥遥相望，诉说心中的爱意。\r\n　　老妇人逐渐开始健忘，吊扇的身上落满灰尘，而花儿也因缺乏水分渐渐枯萎。面对虚弱的爱人，吊扇心中甚感担忧……","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>电风扇和花</li><li><span>话数: </span>1</li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/20643\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">Bill Plympton</a></li><li><span>上映年度: </span>2005</li><li><span>片长: </span>7:22</li><li><span>编剧: </span>Dan O'Shannon</li>","collection":{"wish":24,"collect":66,"doing":2,"dropped":2},"tags":[{"name":"短片","count":36},{"name":"2005","count":19},{"name":"爱情","count":16},{"name":"欧美","count":13},{"name":"美国","count":11},{"name":"治愈","count":6},{"name":"动画短片","count":5},{"name":"真爱","count":3},{"name":"恋&爱","count":3},{"name":"比尔·普莱姆顿","count":3},{"name":"BillPlympton","count":2},{"name":"平静","count":2},{"name":"2021","count":2},{"name":"非日本","count":1},{"name":"Bill.Plympton","count":1},{"name":"七星","count":1},{"name":"映画","count":1},{"name":"剧场版","count":1},{"name":"2005年","count":1},{"name":"小故事","count":1},{"name":"US","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":47189,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/47189","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"The fan and the flower","name_cn":"花与电风扇","duration":"07:21","airdate":"2005","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"staff":[{"id":20643,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/b4/07/20643_prsn_AZRzO.jpg","name":"比尔·普莱姆顿","desc":"导演"}],"like":[{"id":14542,"name":"精神分裂症","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/d0/5a/14542_5NK5N.jpg"},{"id":13379,"name":"雨之城","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/99/3e/13379_0R0E4.jpg"},{"id":11658,"name":"回忆积木小屋","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/5f/df/11658_89hgY.jpg"},{"id":12351,"name":"滑过河面的风","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/26/9e/12351_ZqKs2.jpg"},{"id